r violation of the related obligations of that recognition.</li></ul></li><li>special recognition conditions:<ul><li>employ at least 1 approved <a href=\"https://www.dev-vlaanderen.be/erkenning-als-technicus-brandbeveiligingsapparatuur\">fire protection equipment technician</a><strong> </strong></li><li>employ a sufficient number of approved fire protection equipment technicians to meet <strong>the expected volume of activity</strong> </li><li>provide evidence that <strong>the necessary tools and procedures</strong> are available to the approved fire protection equipment technician</li></ul></li></ul><h3>Your company already has European certification as a fire protection equipment company? </h3><p>A company that has already obtained a <strong>European certificate as a fire protection equipment company</strong> outside the Flemish Region can also obtain the Flemish certificate of recognition as a fire protection equipment company. However, the company must register with the Flemish authorities before it starts working in the Flemish Region. </p><h3>Period of validity and obligations</h3><p>The recognition is valid for <strong>an indefinite period</strong>. However, the recognised company must fulfil some obligations (= user requirements) in order to maintain the recognition.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.dev-vlaanderen.be/informatie-voor-een-koeltechnisch-bedrijf\">More info on the obligations for recognised companies for fire protection equipment</a>.</p>"},"naam":{"nl":"Voorwaarden","nl-BE-x-formal":"Voorwaarden","en-x-generated":"Conditions","en":"Requirements","nl-BE-x-generated-informal":"Voorwaarden"},"@type":"Voorwaarde","order":0}],"procedures":[{"naam":{"en-x-generated":"Procedure","nl-BE-x-generated-informal":"Procedure","nl-BE-x-formal":"Procedure","en":"Procedure","nl":"Procedure"},"beschrijving":{"nl":"<h3>Uw bedrijf heeft nog geen Europees certificaat als bedrijf voor brandbeveiligingsapparatuur </h3><p>Vraag uw erkenning aan bij de Vlaamse overheid:</p>