ren.be/natuur-milieu-en-klimaat/erkenning-als-technicus-deskundige-opleidingscentrum-of-labo/erkenningenloket-omgeving\">online recognition desk of the Department of Environment and Spatial Development</a> (click on \"Go to the recognition desk\"; register with eID).</p><p>Attach the following information to your notification:</p><ul><li>a copy of the European certificate as a refrigeration company in Dutch, French, German or English</li><li>the official name of the company</li><li>the company number of the company. If the company does not have a company number, provide the address of the registered office and the VAT number of the company.</li><li>a general telephone number and e-mail address</li></ul><p>If you do not have a Belgian eID, you must send your notification by registered letter to the Department of Environment and Spatial Development, Boulevard du Roi Albert II 20/bus 8, 1000 Brussels, for the attention of Team Acknowledgements, GOP Division.</p><p>Recognition will take effect on the date on which you provide all this information to the authorities. The company will be included in <a href=\"https://datasets.omgeving.vlaanderen.be/be.vl.omgeving.erkenningen.distribution.bedrijven_koeltechniek.pdf\">the list of approved refrigeration companies</a>. </p>"},"@type":"Procedure","order":0}],"kosten":[{"beschrijving":{"en-x-generated":"<p>The approved refrigeration company has to pay an <a href=\"https://www.dev-vlaanderen.be/vlarel-retributies\">annual fee</a> for monitoring the approval. The approved refrigeration company receives an invoice for this by post at the beginning of the calendar year.</p><ul><li>For <strong>2024 </strong>, this fee is: <strong>€137</strong>.</li><li>The amount is indexed annually.</li></ul>","nl":"<p>Het erkende koeltechnisch bedrijf moet een <a href=\"https://www.dev-vlaanderen.be/vlarel-retributies\">jaarlijkse retributie</a> betalen voor het toezicht op de erkenning. Het erkende koeltechnisch bedrijf krijgt daarvoor in het beg